<!--
Working as of 30/04/2026. This has:
- 2 discoveries: 1 for reg to identify servers, 1 to find services.
- 1 unit monitor for all services that alerts for each service down
- 1 dependency monitor (doesn't alert) so health rolls up to Windows Computer.

Health roles up to Print Service > Print Server > Windows Computer.
-->
<ManagementPack ContentReadable="true" SchemaVersion="2.0" OriginalSchemaVersion="1.1" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform">
